OL,4,BAgents threaten Fifa with legal action
OL,5,Bover transfer payment cap plans
OL,6, Leading agents including Mino Raiola,
OL,7, Jorge Mendes and Jonathan Barnett have
OL,8, threatened Fifa with legal action over
OL,9, plans for a cap on transfer payments.
OL,11,FIn September, Fifa announced plans to
OL,12,Flimit agents of the selling club to a
OL,13,Fmaximum of 10% of the transfer fee.
OL,15,FIn addition, Fifa want a 3% cap of the
OL,16,Fplayer's fee and 3% of the player's fee
OL,17,Ffor agents of the buying club.
OL,19,F"We want fairness," Barnett countered.
OL,20,F"Fifa should recognise us and treat us
OL,21,Fin a proper manner."
